OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1772554282
OL,3,CHalf a million pounds worth of cocaine
OL,4,Cstopped from hitting streets
OL,6,FMore than half a million pounds worth
OL,7,Fof cocaine has been stopped from
OL,8,Fhitting the streets following a drugs
OL,9,Finvestigation.
OL,11,FBradley Pritchard, 33, was stopped by
OL,12,Fofficers, who had been building a case
OL,13,Fagainst him, in Johnstone Road, Thorpe
OL,14,FBay in Southend, Essex in November
OL,15,F2025.
OL,17,FHe told police he was "just driving a
OL,18,Fwork car" and gave them an old address.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
