PN,41602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1772554282
OL,3,CHalf a million pounds worth of cocaine
OL,4,Cstopped from hitting streets
OL,6,FA search of the car led to the
OL,7,Fdiscovery of #12,500 worth of cocaine
OL,8,Fin a Tesco bag for life, and his true
OL,9,Fhome address of in Exford Avenue,
OL,10,FSouthend.
OL,12,FWhen that property was searched,
OL,13,Fofficers found four 1kg blocks of
OL,14,Fcocaine hidden in a pink suitcase
OL,15,Finside a shed in the garden.
OL,17,FA further 1kg block was found in a
OL,18,Flarge plastic tub alongside assorted
OL,19,Fdrug packing paraphernalia.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1772554282
OL,3,CHalf a million pounds worth of cocaine
OL,4,Cstopped from hitting streets
OL,6,FThere was also 100g of cocaine in a
OL,7,Fbedroom wardrobe.
OL,9,FIn total, he was found with around
OL,10,F5kg, worth around #512,500 of the
OL,11,FClass A drug, which was bound for the
OL,12,Fstreets of south Essex.
OL,14,FPritchard was charged with two counts
OL,15,Fof possession of a Class A drug with
OL,16,Fintent to supply.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
