PN,41604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1772554282
OL,3,CHalf a million pounds worth of cocaine
OL,4,Cstopped from hitting streets
OL,6,FHe admitted playing a significant role
OL,7,Fin the drug supply operation and was
OL,8,Fsentenced at Basildon Crown Court on
OL,9,FThursday 26 February to five years and
OL,10,Ffour months in prison.
OL,12,FOthers involved in this wider
OL,13,Foperation have already been convicted,
OL,14,Fwith some still awaiting sentencing.
OL,16,FPritchard will also be pursued for his
OL,17,Fcriminal proceeds by our financial
OL,18,Finvestigators.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
