FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1772554282
OL,3,CHalf a million pounds worth of cocaine
OL,4,Cstopped from hitting streets
OL,6,FDet Sgt Leo Fordham said: "Pritchard
OL,7,Fwas very calm when his car was stopped
OL,8,Fin November and he did everything he
OL,9,Fcould to throw officers of the scent.
OL,11,F"But it didn't work. We found 5kg of
OL,12,Fcocaine which we were able to link to
OL,13,Fhim without question, and he ended up
OL,14,Fwith no option but to admit the
OL,15,Foffences against him."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/5
